channel.title: Compiling Error Taking New Hit Marks From InsidiaX
channel.description:
Hello, I was taking the new Hit Mark things from InsidiaX source + Client and I came across some errors: [code=java]src\server\model\players\packets\CombatAssistant.java:17: duplicate class: serve r.model.players.CombatAssistant public class CombatAssistant{ ^ src\server\model\players\packets\CombatAssistant.java:14: package server.model.p layers.Hit does not exist import server.model.players.Hit.CombatType; ^ src\server\model\players\Client.java:1251: cannot find symbol symbol : variable INCREASE_SPECIAL_AMOUNT_WITH_RING location: class server.Config if(System.currentTimeMillis() - specDelay > Config.INCREASE_SPEC IAL_AMOUNT_WITH_RING && playerEquipment[playerRing] == 19669) { ^ src\server\model\players\CombatAssistant.java:2437: cannot find symbol symbol : method handCannonDestory() location: class server.model.players.Client c.handCannonDestory(); ^ src\server\model\players\ActionHandler.java:1987: cannot find symbol symbol : method openPlayerShop(server.model.players.Client) location: class server.model.shops.ShopAssistant c.getShops().openPlayerShop(c); ^ src\server\model\players\skills\Summoning.java:57: cannot find symbol symbol : method Frame34(int,int,int,int) location: class server.model.players.PlayerAssistant c.getPA().Frame34(7423, c.storeditems[k] , k, 1); ^ src\server\model\players\skills\Summoning.java:63: cannot find symbol symbol : method Frame34(int,int,int,int) location: class server.model.players.PlayerAssistant c.getPA().Frame34(7423, -1, k, 1); ^ src\server\model\npcs\NPCHandler.java:3909: cannot find symbol symbol : method addCharge(server.model.players.Client) location: class server.model.players.CombatAssistant c.getCombat().addCharge(c); ^ Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 8 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code] Note: These are errors in my source folder. Please tell me what I need to fix these, I'm a beginning coder :$
Thanks for reading, ~K l 4 w s
